  <div>
    <p><img alt="English organization" src="/upload/NHD/Organisasjonskart/NHD_orgkart_engelsk_08.JPG" usemap="#FPMap0" border="0" /><map id="FPMap0" name="FPMap0"><area shape="rect" alt="Minister of Trade and Industry Trond Giske" coords="177,163,309,186" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/minister-of-trade-and-industry-trond-gis.html?id=582212" /><area shape="rect" alt="Other political staff" coords="178,192,311,210" href=" http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/Other-political-staff.html?id=731" /><area shape="rect" alt="Administrative" coords="14,280,74,298" href=" http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/administrative-department.html?id=1532" /><area shape="rect" alt="Ownership" coords="91,272,149,302" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/ownership-department.html?id=1522" /><area shape="rect" alt="Economic Policy Department" coords="164,275,236,303" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/economic-policy-deartement.html?id=528217" /><area shape="rect" alt="Maritime Department" coords="254,279,306,301" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/maritime-departement.html?id=528219" /><area shape="rect" alt="Trade Policy Department" coords="332,276,392,301" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/trade-policy-departement.html?id=528222" /><area shape="rect" alt="Research and Innovation Department" coords="408,274,494,304" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/about-the-ministry/organisation/Departments/research-and-innovation-department.html?id=528252" /><area shape="rect" alt="Communications" coords="90,225,174,248" href="http://www.regjeringen.no/en/dep/nhd/press-centre.html?id=712" /></map> </p>
<p><br />The Ministry of Trade and Industry has six departments. The Press and Communications Division is part of the Secretary General’s staff.</p>
<p>The Ministry is headed by the Minister of Trade and Industry. The other political staff consists of three State Secretaries and one Political Advisor.</p>
